，如果tune到嘅話富士使乜賣相機，賣software得啦<br />\n<br />\n就算擺入lightroom用返富士底片模擬，啲顏色一樣有分別</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實可以話係一種色彩，analogue既。<br />\n佢包含唔知幾多種基因去表達一系列顏色。<br />\n<br />\n夾硬用數碼去tune，只是循一個方向去&ldquo;迫近&ldquo;個效果，而非真是完全&ldquo;推&ldquo;到一樣。<br />\n<br />\n如果推得到仲邊有人影菲林/即影即有丫？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/38.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我都係由數碼走向菲林。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d123dbdfe87b72e006d2b4bbbb49d6b646f0aed","tid":229843,"uid":71341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T02:36:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f36168093dff534585f8421cc88ba146ce3cac51","tid":229843,"uid":78399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T02:43:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>屌你地想愈黎愈多買fuji?<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係擺上嚟就爽手啦，我真係未聽過入完富士有死貨啊，我夠識話有百鳩幾個朋友入完富士喊三聲，佢地買完body搶唔到鏡嚟買啊，而家個個等緊人放二手啊，冇鏡用影唔到相好慘架嘛係咪？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj